# ATM Verification Framework for Secure Transaction Processing

A hardware verification project that models secure ATM transactions using a Verilog Finite State Machine (FSM) and validates its correctness through an automated Python-based verification framework.

---

## Features

* 12-state Verilog FSM implementation
* Card authentication and PIN verification
* 3-attempt account lockout
* Withdrawal limits and insufficient balance detection
* Automated testbench generation
* Randomized and edge-case testing
* State and transition coverage reporting
* HTML dashboard and waveform visualization
* One-command regression execution

