---

## Running the Project

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd ATM-Verification-Framework
```

Run the complete verification flow:

```bash
python run_demo.py
```

Run unit tests:

```bash
python -m unittest discover tests -v
```

Generate coverage report:

```bash
python scripts/generate_coverage.py
```

Run a single simulation:

```bash
python -m sim.run_native
```

